Swyft/Rion/Hysteria

Swyft:

Swyft nods in acknowledgement, realizing that must be who he was taking her 
to see. However, she should have mentioned her name earlier, but now was as 
good a time as any:

"I believe I forgot to mention my name. I'm Swyft."

* * * * *

Rion:

"Woah!"

The ground shifted and fell out from beneath him as Rion shot forward and 
tumbled head over heels down the steep slope. He grunted and groaned as he 
toppled down the hill. Eventually he was able to get his feet underneath him 
and slow his descent, skidding to a rather abrupt stop just before colliding 
with an extremely large bush. In the distance he could hear gunfire and was 
barely able to make out the ouline of a very large ship. A ship!

"Diana! Do you see that?!"

He pointed into the distance at the twisted hunk of metal.

* * * * *

Hysteria:

Hysteria finished welding the new panel shut and moved on to do some basic 
programming with the computers. There were still a few bugs to work out, but 
as long as nothing exploded for the next ten minutes she should be able to 
get it fixed.
